<p><i>Submitted October 15, 2019</i></p>
<p><b> Postdoctoral Fellowships<br />
Stanford Center on Philanthropy and Civil Society</b></p>
 
<p>The Stanford Center on Philanthropy and Civil Society brings promising new scholars to Stanford University for 1-2 year appointments as postdoctoral fellows.
 Currently Stanford PACS is accepting applications for two postdoctoral fellowship opportunities for the 2020-21 academic year:</p>
 
<ul>
<li>The Program on Democracy and the Internet (<a href="https://pacscenter.stanford.edu/research/program-on-democracy-and-the-internet/pdi-post-doctoral-fellowship/" rel="nofollow">pacscenter.stanford.edu/research/program-on-democracy-and-the-internet/pdi-post-doctoral-fellowship/</a>)</li>
