<p>Research areas of special interest include:</p>
<p>Human in the loop or knowledge-enhanced AI, deep learning, natural language processing, question-answering/conversational AI, brain-inspired computing, semantic/cognitive/perceptual computing;
AI and Big data &mdash; including social, sensor, biological, and health &mdash; and scalable computing/analysis of big data;
